trans-unit.source: List Available Extensions
trans-unit.target: List Available Extensions

trans-unit.source: The <languageKeyword>List Available Extensions</languageKeyword> operation lists the extensions that are available to add to your cloud service.
trans-unit.target: The <languageKeyword>List Available Extensions</languageKeyword> operation lists the extensions that are available to add to your cloud service.

trans-unit.source: In Microsoft Azure, a process can run as an extension of a cloud service.
trans-unit.target: In Microsoft Azure, a process can run as an extension of a cloud service.

trans-unit.target: Request

trans-unit.target: The <languageKeyword>List Available Extensions</languageKeyword> request may be specified as follows.

trans-unit.source: ReplicationCompleted
trans-unit.target: ReplicationCompleted

trans-unit.source: Indicates whether the version of the extension has been replicated to all regions.
trans-unit.target: Indicates whether the version of the extension has been replicated to all regions.

trans-unit.source: Possible values are:
trans-unit.target: Possible values are:

trans-unit.source: <languageKeyword>true</languageKeyword> if the extension version can be used to create or update a deployment; otherwise, <languageKeyword>false</languageKeyword> indicating that the version of the extension is not ready to be used in all regions.
trans-unit.target: <languageKeyword>true</languageKeyword> if the extension version can be used to create or update a deployment; otherwise, <languageKeyword>false</languageKeyword> indicating that the version of the extension is not ready to be used in all regions.

trans-unit.source: The <languageKeyword>ReplicationCompleted</languageKeyword> element is only available using version 2014-04-01 or higher.
